description:
Every year, unicorns from all over the world gather for the Grand Unicorn Convention, a dazzling celebration of all things Unicorn. This year, however, Twilight faces an unexpected dilemma. As an Alicorn, she fears her presence may overshadow the convention's focus on unicorns. But Rarity is determined not to let her friend miss out on the beloved tradition.
https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
https://x.com/thetamers12345
